{
  "name": "Rappity, Rap, Tag Team Attack [B-Rank]",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/squares-3d-green.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;You and another allied creature who begins combat with the same hostile enemy, that shares this trait, becomes a tag team duo. As a full turn action, taken on each tag team duo's turn in the same round, both simultaneously cast a Jutsu with the Combination Keyword at the beginning of the following round, regardless of the initiative count. This jutsu's casting cannot be reacted to and deals bonus damage equal to the casters combined level. (Recharge 5-6)&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:13241,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;6&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:3}]},&quot;7&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;8&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:3}]},&quot;10&quot;:1,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Georgia&quot;,&quot;16&quot;:9}\">You and another allied creature who begins combat with the same hostile enemy, that shares this trait, becomes a tag team duo. <br />As a full turn action, taken on each tag team duo's turn in the same round, both simultaneously cast a Jutsu with the Combination Keyword at the beginning of the following round, regardless of the initiative count. <br />This jutsu's casting cannot be reacted to and deals bonus damage equal to the casters combined level. <br />(Recharge 5-6)</span></p>",
